The social map of the Ivanovo region is recognized as an electronic means of payment .
The changes include preserving the benefits of public passenger transport .
On September 24 , is changing the order of concessionary travel organization citizens using the social map of the Ivanovo region .
According to the press service of the Russian government on the Ivanovo region , the changes include preserving benefits for travel in public passenger transport and bring social card payments scheme in accordance with the requirements of the Federal Law No. 161 of the federal law &quot; on the national payment system &quot; .
The social map of the Ivanovo region is recognized as an electronic means of payment .
Accordingly , changing the conditions of its application .
So , the limit of replenishment is now not travel as before , and the amount of cash , with saving winter and summer periods - no more than 400 rubles in winter , in summer - no more than 800 roubles for the current month .
Now owners of social cards issued in transport receipts will need to keep track of the number of remaining trips , and the rest of the money .
The cost of concessionary travel for citizens is 1 / 2 of the current tariff from the carrier .
The remaining half of the cost of travel reimburses the regional budget .
The schedule of replenishment social cash card remains the same - the number of the previous month from 24 to 23 the number of the current month .
The new order of social travel card will have a number of advantages .
So , there is the opportunity to keep a detailed record of spending money on social card with an accuracy of kopeks .
In addition , there is a possibility of returning credited , but unspent money .
Add also that the settlement scheme with carriers becomes transparent , as now half of the fare paid by the citizen , and the same amount to offset the budget carrier .
No commission when making the cash card will not be charged .
In turn , Vasily silkin , zamestetel head of the Department of road and transport of the Ivanovo region , reported that in 2014 in the region was committed more than 33 million trips using social card , 2015 - m - almost 25 million trips .
In the regional budget for granting preferential travel for citizens using social card provided more than 470 million rubles .
As of September 1 , the amount of compensation for these purposes was more than 312 million rubles .
