The head of the UN declares that there is no military solution in Syria
Secretary General Ban Ki - moon said in response to Russia &apos;s military support of Syria , which for nearly five years of conflict , &quot; there is no military solution &quot; and the growth of weapons will only exacerbate violence and suffering for millions of people .
The head of the UN again called for all participants , including the divided UN Security Council to unite and support inclusive talks to find a political solution .
